{"title":"Bluegrass Vanguard is a Feature-Packed Lightweight Full Face Enduro Helmet","link":"https://bikerumor.com/bluegrass-vanguard-full-face-enduro-helmet/","date":1685602800000,"content":"<p>Bluegrass has filled a gaping hole in its helmet lineup with an all-new, lightweight full face helmet for enduro racing. We don’t have our hands on one just yet, but at a claimed 725 grams for a MIPS-equipped size medium, the Bluegrass Vanguard Core looks to be striking a good balance between protection, weight and ventilation. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>On top of its ASTM 1952-15/2032-15 certification for downhill mountain biking, and its NTA 8776 certification for eBiking, the Vanguard Core also gets a 5 Star rating from the independent helmet testers at Virginia Tech. Its actual score? Virginia Tech don’t publish that until the helmet is available in stores so, not until early July.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-tests-impact.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"503\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-tests-impact-800x503.jpg\" alt=\"bluegrass vanguard mtb full face helmet testing\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-tests-impact-800x503.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-tests-impact-297x187.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-tests-impact-120x75.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-tests-impact-768x483.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-tests-impact-1536x966.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-tests-impact.jpg 1600w\" /></a><figcaption>Like many brands, Bluegrass and their parent company, MET, also do a bunch of in-house testing – see some <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/designing-safe-bike-helmets-test-certification-requirements/\" target=\"_blank\">videos of that here</a></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Priced at $350 USD, the Vanguard Core nears the top-end of the spectrum for a helmet in the lightweight full face enduro lid category, but it boasts a couple of neat features that, if well-executed, could make the extra dollars worth it. Here’s an overview.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmet-enduro-side.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmet-enduro-side-800x800.jpg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmet-enduro-side-800x800.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmet-enduro-side-297x297.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmet-enduro-side-120x120.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmet-enduro-side-768x768.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmet-enduro-side-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmet-enduro-side.jpg 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmettopview.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmettopview-800x800.jpg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmettopview-800x800.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmettopview-297x297.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmettopview-120x120.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmettopview-768x768.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmettopview-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmettopview.jpg 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmet-backoffset.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmet-backoffset-800x800.jpg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmet-backoffset-800x800.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmet-backoffset-297x297.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmet-backoffset-120x120.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmet-backoffset-768x768.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmet-backoffset-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmet-backoffset.jpg 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Bluegrass Vanguard Core Full Face Enduro Helmet</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The Bluegrass Vanguard is available in a MIPS-equipped Core Edition that retails at $350 USD (330 €), or a more basic version that lacks any rotational impact protection – that one comes in at a more affordable price point of 270 €. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>It’s not just MIPS that sets them apart; the Core Edition also benefits from a removable mud-grill that covers the main vent on the chin guard, while the basic model lacks one entirely. The Core Edition also gets a Fidlock buckle at the chinstrap, whereas the basic model has an “easy-to-use ratchet buckle”.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-top-vents.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"503\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-top-vents-800x503.jpg\" alt=\"bluegrass vanguard full face enduro helmet\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-top-vents-800x503.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-top-vents-297x187.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-top-vents-120x75.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-top-vents-768x483.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-top-vents-1536x966.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-top-vents.jpg 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Aside from those points, the two helmets are identical. A polycarbonate shell sits at the exterior with an EPS layer underneath taking charge of impact absorption. It is of the modern day in-mold construction.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Vanguard boasts an impressive 24 vents with internal air channeling, something that has become a bit of a must-have in recent years with the rise of enduro racing. It has spurred on the creation of this category of helmet that needs to offer downhill-level protection in a package that is light enough and well ventilated enough to be worn on all-day missions in the heat of summer.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-fixed-chinguard-astm-approved-dh.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-fixed-chinguard-astm-approved-dh-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"vbluegrass vanguard full face enduro helmet astm certified chinbar\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-fixed-chinguard-astm-approved-dh-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-fixed-chinguard-astm-approved-dh-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-fixed-chinguard-astm-approved-dh-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-fixed-chinguard-astm-approved-dh-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-fixed-chinguard-astm-approved-dh-1536x1023.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-fixed-chinguard-astm-approved-dh-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-fixed-chinguard-astm-approved-dh.jpg 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Bluegrass supply two sets of cheek pads with the Vanguard and Vanguard Core, offering up different thicknesses – 25mm and 35mm – to fit varying jaw shapes. Importantly, these are shaped such that they don’t block airflow through the massive air vent that runs down the side of the chin guard.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Bluegrass-Vanguard-cheek-pad-positions.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Bluegrass-Vanguard-cheek-pad-positions-800x1200.jpg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Bluegrass-Vanguard-cheek-pad-positions-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Bluegrass-Vanguard-cheek-pad-positions-200x300.jpg 200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Bluegrass-Vanguard-cheek-pad-positions-80x120.jpg 80w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Bluegrass-Vanguard-cheek-pad-positions-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Bluegrass-Vanguard-cheek-pad-positions-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Bluegrass-Vanguard-cheek-pad-positions-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Bluegrass-Vanguard-cheek-pad-positions.jpg 1600w\" /></a><figcaption>There are two possible positions for the cheek pad too, which should help riders dial in a good fit</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Though the construction may make you wonder otherwise, the Vanguard chin piece is actually fixed in place. It will flex inwards to a maximum of 30mm during an impact; that’s in the context of the maximum of 60mm flex permitted by the ASTM testing.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The peak also has a fixed position, though it is designed to break away easily in the event of a crash to prevent it causing undesirable neck rotation.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For retention, the Vanguard relies upon the so-called Safe-T Heta system which can be cinched down via a dial at the rear. The position of this 360° head belt can be adjusted vertically, too. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmet-green-fluid.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmet-green-fluid-800x800.jpg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmet-green-fluid-800x800.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmet-green-fluid-297x297.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmet-green-fluid-120x120.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmet-green-fluid-768x768.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmet-green-fluid-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmet-green-fluid.jpg 1600w\" /></a><figcaption>Vanguard Core Edition Green Fluid</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmet-blue-fluid.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmet-blue-fluid-800x800.jpg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmet-blue-fluid-800x800.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmet-blue-fluid-297x297.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmet-blue-fluid-120x120.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmet-blue-fluid-768x768.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmet-blue-fluid-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmet-blue-fluid.jpg 1600w\" /></a><figcaption>Vanguard Core Edition Blue Fluid</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmet-black.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmet-black-800x800.jpg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmet-black-800x800.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmet-black-297x297.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmet-black-120x120.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmet-black-768x768.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmet-black-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-core-mips-mtb-fullface-helmet-black.jpg 1600w\" /></a><figcaption>Vanguard Core Edition Black</figcaption></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>Pricing &amp; Availability</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The Bluegrass Vanguard Core retails at 330 € | £290 | US $350 | CAD $450 | AUS $450, and is available in White Black Matt, Black Matt Glossy, Blue Fluid Matt and Green Fluid Matt. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Meanwhile, the more basic model, simply named the Vanguard, is priced at 270 €. That one is available in Black Matt, Blue Ochre Matt, Solar Gray Matt and Lime Matt. Both models are due to be available this coming July.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-black.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-black-800x800.jpg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-black-800x800.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-black-297x297.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-black-120x120.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-black-768x768.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-black-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-black.jpg 1600w\" /></a><figcaption>Vanguard Black</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-blue-ochre.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-blue-ochre-800x800.jpg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-blue-ochre-800x800.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-blue-ochre-297x297.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-blue-ochre-120x120.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-blue-ochre-768x768.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-blue-ochre-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-blue-ochre.jpg 1600w\" /></a><figcaption>Vanguard Blue Ochre</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-lime.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-lime-800x800.jpg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-lime-800x800.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-lime-297x297.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-lime-120x120.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-lime-768x768.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-lime-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/bluegrass-vanguard-mtb-fullface-helmet-lime.jpg 1600w\" /></a><figcaption>Vanguard Lime</figcaption></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<h4>Vanguard Specifications</h4>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Weight M size (Vanguard Core): 725g</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Weight M size (Vanguard): 690g</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Sizes: S (52-56cm) | M (56-58cm) | L (58-61cm)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Certifications: ASTM 1952-15/2032-15 | NTA 8776 | CE | AS/NZS | US</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure><div>\n\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.met-helmets.com/en/bluegrass/\" target=\"_blank\">met-helmets.com/bluegrass</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/bluegrass-vanguard-full-face-enduro-helmet/\">Bluegrass Vanguard is a Feature-Packed Lightweight Full Face Enduro Helmet</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Jessie-May Morgan","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"6c423967bb22e14ebfb555ed52f6ca9e979e060a14f9763dabf41d73b7db7a12","category":"Cycling"}